    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行高管表示，目标瞄准富有的外籍人士，看好亚洲公司推动欧洲业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-targets-wealthy-expats-bullish-asian-firms-drive-europe-unit-exec-says-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行欧洲业务主管押注于地区财富的增长和亚洲企业客户的海外扩张，以提高其部门对集团利润的贡献，此前汇丰银行经过多年的重新启动，将业务从落后者转变为利润引擎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-targets-wealthy-expats-bullish-asian-firms-drive-europe-unit-exec-says-2024-04-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦表示，美国不会接受中国进口商品，从而摧毁新产业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-meets-with-chinas-central-bank-chief-presses-case-excess-capacity-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周一警告中国，华盛顿不会接受新产业因中国进口产品而遭受重创，她结束了为期四天的会议，敦促北京控制过剩的工业产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-meets-with-chinas-central-bank-chief-presses-case-excess-capacity-2024-04-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国世茂因未能偿还2.02亿美元贷款而面临清算诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-faces-liquidation-suit-over-failure-pay-202-mln-loan-2024-04-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国开发商世茂集团周一表示，中国建设银行（亚洲）已就其未偿债务在香港提出清算申请，这是国有银行在房地产低迷时期采取此类法律行动的罕见案例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-faces-liquidation-suit-over-failure-pay-202-mln-loan-2024-04-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 00:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
